<title>USA: Platinum Software acquires software co.</title>
<headline>Platinum Software acquires software co.</headline>
<dateline>IRVINE, Calif. 1997-06-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Platinum Software Corp said Monday it has a definitive agreement to acquire privately held Clientele Software Inc, which provides customer service software.</p>
<p>As part of the deal, Platinum will issue up to 1.1 million shares of common stock for all outstanding shares and stock options of Clientele.</p>
<p>The acquisition is structured as a merger and is being accounted for as a pooling of interests, based on an exchange of stock with an effective closing today, it said.</p>
<p>Platinum Software develops and markets client/server software products for corporations worldwide.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
